OL,4,Cover Gaza ceasefire vote chaos
OL,6,FThe row erupted when Sir Lindsay
OL,7,Fdecided the Commons would first vote
OL,8,Fon Labour's amendment before moving on
OL,9,Fto further votes on the SNP's original
OL,10,Fmotion and then a Government proposal
OL,11,Fseeking an "immediate humanitarian
OL,12,Fpause".
OL,14,FHe disregarded warnings from the House
OL,15,Fof Commons Clerk over the
OL,16,Funprecedented nature of the move,
OL,17,Fwhich provoked uproar in the chamber.
OL,19,Fended up passing unopposed without a
OL,20,Fformal vote after the Government
OL,21,Fpulled its participation.
