OL,6,FIt marked the first time the Commons
OL,7,Fformally backed an immediate ceasefire
OL,8,Fin Gaza, though the Government does
OL,9,Fnot have to adopt the position as the
OL,10,Fvote is not binding.
OL,12,FThe SNP were ultimately unable to vote
OL,13,Fon their proposition calling for "an
OL,14,Fimmediate ceasefire", which was meant
OL,15,Fto be the focus of their Opposition
OL,16,FDay.
