OL,3,CCommons Speaker faces calls to resign
OL,4,Cover Gaza ceasefire vote chaos
OL,6,FSNP MPs and some Conservatives walked
OL,7,Fout of the debate in protest at the
OL,8,FSpeaker's handling of the matter in
OL,9,Fextraordinary scenes.
OL,11,FAfter calls for him to return to the
OL,12,Fchamber to explain his move, Sir
OL,13,FLindsay apologised to MPs and vowed to
OL,14,Fhold talks with senior party figures.
OL,16,FAmid shouts of "resign", he said: "I
OL,17,Fthought I was doing the right thing
OL,18,Fand the best thing, and I regret it,
OL,19,Fand I apologise for how it's ended up."
