OL,6,FHe also called for an investigation as
OL,7,Fhe appeared to suggest Sir Keir and
OL,8,FLabour's chief whip had exerted
OL,9,Fpressure on Sir Lindsay, a former
OL,10,FLabour MP, ahead of his decision to
OL,11,Fpick the party's amendment for debate.
OL,13,FHad the Speaker not chosen it, Labour
OL,14,FMPs in favour of a ceasefire could
OL,15,Fhave been pushed to back the SNP
OL,16,Fmotion, in a repeat of a major
OL,17,Frebellion against the Labour
OL,18,Fleadership in November.
